        <Brief>
            <p><strong>Index of Biblical Notes in English</strong></p>

            <p>
                These Bible Notes are useful to understand some themes that
                God's enemies have tried to twist, or themes that are difficult
                to interpret.
            </p>

            <p>
                It is beneficial to read them. You can use all the material in
                here to help others, especially to help members of your church.
            </p>

            <p>
                <strong
                    >We are going to add new Bible Notes as often as possible;
                    therefore visit us frequently</strong
                >. <strong
                    >If you think I have a mistake in a Biblical Note</strong
                >, please, send me your opinion and the arguments that can back
                it up. I will appreciate it very much. I also like to learn from
                others.
            </p>

            <p>
                Also if you would like some special issue to be addressed in a
                Biblical Note, just leave me a message at the following e-mail
                address: ramonaleman@yahoo<strong>.</strong>com to R. L.
                Serralta Nogués.
            </p>
        </Brief>

